/span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">toMonoidalCategoryStruct</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝒞</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v, u}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory\">MonoidalCategory</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategoryStruct\">MonoidalCategoryStruct</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.toMonoidalCategoryStruct","kind":"def","line":160,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.toMonoidalCategoryStruct","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.lean#L160-L208"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">𝒞</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v, u}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategoryStruct\">CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategoryStruct</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max u v)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"In a monoidal category, we can take the tensor product of objects, `X ⊗ Y` and of morphisms\n`f ⊗ₘ g`.\nTensor product does not need to be strictly associative on objects, but there is a\nspecified associator, `α_ X Y Z : (X ⊗ Y) ⊗ Z ≅ X ⊗ (Y ⊗ Z)`. There is a tensor unit `𝟙_ C`,\nwith specified left and right unitor isomorphisms `λ_ X : 𝟙_ C ⊗ X ≅ X` and `ρ_ X : X ⊗ 𝟙_ C ≅ X`.\nThese associators and unitors satisfy the pentagon and triangle equations. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory","kind":"class","line":151,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.lean#L151-L208"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.Pentagon\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">Pentagon</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_